{"tid":1702001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武要智取 唔係死守","createTime":"2019-11-09T12:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T12:57:31.000Z","uid":338130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52a90a50d287373e74147837b9e4cd18055b4462","tid":1702001,"uid":338130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:56:42.000Z","msg":"其實琴日將軍澳開花係送頭<br />\n根本係狗撚我地 多過我地撚狗<br />\n我連續打咗尚德幾日 可以講根本無乜資源再打<br />\n琴日既傘陣 十把遮都無 水都無 中tg根本無位走<br />\n將軍澳區自己team手足講明琴日唔係尚德開打<br />\n要打都係警察落地先打 其他區手足死都set Rb <br />\n引曬啲警察聚曬尚德 上面仲好撚多人悼念緊吖屌<br />\n一個tg過嚟 上面有老有嫩 真係跌多個落嚟都唔出奇<br />\n我明大家好嬲 但唔可以叫晒上面啲人陪我地一齊死<br />\n同埋唔好燒電箱 因為真係俾人拉都睇唔到樣 <br />\n不完美但可改善 同埋真係唔係人多就有用<br />\n將軍澳根本冇乜地方可以匿埋 通常都係上樓多<br />\n十八區手足入嚟根本無位走 一定會俾人圍捕<br />\n可能咁講好衰仔 但真係麻煩聽下打慣自己區嘅人講嘢 唔好喺度嘈 聽下人哋意見 <br />\n出得嚟都係想一齊返到去 一個都不能少"},{"pid":"5d2c2ab7e418d0fb2541f57cf36a8bbc7e08b58f","tid":1702001,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">幫手Rt + like </span><br />\n<br />\nSenator Scott嘅tweet嚴重唔夠人推，佢係法案好主要嘅推手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=d292e984\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006&h=b1cbde8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006</a><br />\n<br />\nSenator Rubio盡心盡力，迫McConnell迫到咁緊都係唔夠多推，希望大家可以幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=1344b748\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&h=d2de161b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846</a>"}]}